order-google-sell-chrome-search-antitrust-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esell%20its%20Chrome%20browser%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20remedy%20in%20the%20case.%20A%20final%20ruling%20in%20the%20case%20is%20expected%20in%20August%2C%20Business%20Insider%20previously%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Donald%20Trump's%20incoming%20administration%2C%20Khan%20will%20be%20replaced%20as%20Chair%20by%20current%20FTC%20Commissioner%20Andrew%20Ferguson%2C%20the%20president-elect%20announced%20in%20December%20on%20Truth%20Social.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Khan%20was%20the%20subject%20of%20intense%20political%20vitriol%20during%20the%20election%20for%20her%20staunch%20antitrust%20enforcement%2C%20Ferguson%2C%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20vowed%20to%20continue%20the%20office's%20mission%20to%20promote%20innovation%20and%20%26quot%3Bend%20Big%20Tech's%20vendetta%20against%20competition%20and%20free%20speech.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20make%20sure%20that%20America%20is%20the%20world's%20technological%20leader%20and%20the%20best%20place%20for%20innovators%20to%20bring%20new%20ideas%20to%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20Ferguson%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-lawsuit%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmazon%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Anthropic%2C%20and%20OpenAI%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fftc-hints-ai-partnerships-antitrust-scrutiny-microsoft-openai-amazon-anthropic-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737376022000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F678c658f10c98eace9130a51%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22or