mp-inauguration-davos-first-day-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EWorld%20Economic%20Forum%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Davos%3Cspan%3E%20doesn't%20begin%20in%20earnest%20until%20later%20on%20Monday%2C%20but%20business%20and%20tech%20leaders%20have%20already%20descended%20on%20the%20Swiss%20mountain%20resort.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAI%2C%20Donald%20Trump's%20reelection%2C%20and%20crypto%20are%20proving%20hot%20topics.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBusiness%20Insider%20is%20on%20the%20ground%20and%20talking%20to%20people.%20This%20is%20what%20we're%20hearing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3ETalk%20of%20AI%20and%20AI%20agents%20is%20already%20in%20full%20swing%20here%2C%20but%20Mihir%20Shukla%2C%20CEO%20of%20Automation%20Anywhere%2C%20believes%20this%20year%20the%20conversation%20is%20turning%20from%20hype%20to%20questions%20about%20practical%20realities.%20%26quot%3BAs%20CEOs%20here%20are%20chasing%20AI%2C%20they%20find%20it%20cool%2C%20but%20the%20job%20is%20to%20find%20value%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI%20in%20an%20interview.%20%26quot%3BI%20know%20this%20is%20cool%2C%20but%20what%20can%20I%20do%20with%20it%3F%20I%20think%20that%20conversation%20happens%20this%20year.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECan%20AI%20do%20his%20job%20yet%3F%20Not%20completely%2C%20but%20he%20admitted%20it%20could%20do%20some.%20A%20fun%20example%3A%20His%20company%20built%20a%20boardroom%20AI%20agent%20and%20trained%20it%20on%20years%20of%20the%20company's%20financial%20information%20and%20presentations.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20able%20to%20match%20patterns%20that%20the%20most%20experienced%20people%20couldn't%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20It%20was%20so%20good%2C%20they%20even%20gave%20the%20AI%20agent%20an%20empty%20seat%20at%20the%20boardroom%20table%20for%20dramatic%20effect.%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3EHugh%20Langley%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20hurdle%20with%20AI%20agents%3A%20How%20do%20companies%20get%20paid%20for%20their%20work%2C%20and%20who%20gets%20the%20credit%2C%20and%20more%20importantly%2C%20the%20revenue%2C%20internally%3F%20Raj%20Sharma%2C%20EY's%20global%20managing%20partner%20for%20growth%20and%20innovation%2C%20told%20BI%20the%20power%20of%20AI%20agents%20is%20forcing%20the%20professional%20services%20giant%20to%20reconsider%20its%20commercial%20model.%20Instead%20of%20just%20charging%20clients%20based%20on%20the%20hours%20and%20resources%20EY%20might%20spend%20on%20a%20project%2C%20Sharma%20said%20with%20AI%20agents%20it%20can%20take%20a%20%26quot%3Bservice-as-a-software%26quot%3B%20approach%20where%20clients%20pay%20based%20on%20outcome.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20issue%20isn't%20just%20external.%20Some%20thought%20needs%20to%20be%20given%20to%20who%20owns%20the%20agents%20and%20is%20responsible%20for%20the%20revenue%20they%20bring%20in.%20%26quot%3BAs%20much%20time%20as%20we%20are%20spending%20on%20the%20technology%20aspect%20of%20these%20things%2C%20the%20whole%20commercial%20model%2C%20the%20risk%20models%20associated%20with%20that%2C%20there's%20an%20equal%20amount%20of%20energy%2C%20at%20least%20companies%20like%20ours%20are%20spending%2C%20to%20say%20'What%20is%20the%20right%20commercial%20model%3F'%26quot%3B%20Sharma%20said.%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3EDan%20DeFrancesco%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20my%20fourth%20Davos%2C%20and%20every%20year%2C%20one%20topic%20seems%20to%20take%20over.%20In%202023%2C%20it%20was%20AI's%20rapid%20rise.%20In%202022%2C%20inflation%20angst%20was%20the%20buzzword.%20This%20year%20is%20a%20three-way%20brawl%20between%20agentic%20AI%2C%20Trump's%20tariff%20talk%2C%20and%20crypto's%20regulatory%20tug-of-war.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECrypto%20isn't%20just%20a%20side%20conversation%20anymore.%20With%20bulls%20celebrating%20bitcoin%20passing%20the%20%24100%2C000%20mark%20and%20regulators%20clashing%20over%20how%20to%20rein%20in%20the%20Wild%20West%20of%20digital%20assets%2C%20crypto%20is%20now%20as%20much%20a%20part%20of%20Davos%20as%20cheese%20and%20fondue%20at%20high-powered%20dinner%20debates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20which%20topic%20will%20dominate%20the%20late-night%20wining%20and%20dining%20and%20daytime-ski%20chatter%3F%20Crypto's%20got%20the%20hype%2C%20AI%20has%20the%20intrigue%2C%20and%20Trump%3F%20He%20can't%20help%20but%20be%20the%20main%20character.%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%94%20Spriha%20Srivastava%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt's%20a%20bit%20warmer%20than%20usual%20in%20the%20mountain%20town%20this%20week%2C%20with%20daily%20highs%20reaching%20the%20mid-to-high%2030s.%20At%20night%2C%20it's%20only%20expected%20to%20drop%20to%20the%20mid-to-high%2020s.%20(The%20daily%20average%20temperature%20for%20the%20town%20is%20typically%20in%20the%20low%2020s.)%20And%20the%20famous%20%26quot%3Bsuits%20and%20boots%26quot%3B%20look%20the%20conference%20has%20become%20known%20for%20won't%20be%20as%20necessary%20this%20week%20with%20no%20snow%20forecast.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20of%20that%20is%20in%20stark%20contrast%20to%20the%20US%2C%20where%20the%20East%20Coast%20is%20dealing%20with%20some%20severe%20cold%20weather%20and%20a%20rare%20snow%20and%20ice%20storm%20threatens%20the%20South.%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3EDan%20DeFrancesco%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20photo%20of%20the%20Promenande%20at%20the%20Davos%20World%20Economic%20Forum%2C%20showing%20a%20sign%20saying%20%26quot%3BIndia%20Bharat%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F678e311a2fcded5e9073e09d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDavos'%20Promenade%20is%20full%20of%20emerging%20economies%20setting%20out%20their%20stalls.%3Cp%3ESpriha%20Srivastava%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWalking%20down%20the%20Promenade%20in%20Davos%20Sunday%20night%2C%20I%20couldn't%20help%20but%20notice%20something%20different%20%E2%80%94%20emerging%20economies%20are%20showing%20up%20in%20a%20bigger%20way%20this%20year.%20Last%20year%2C%20India%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia%20made%20a%20splash%2C%20staking%20out%20prime%20real%20estate%20along%20this%20iconic%20stretch%20where%20you're%20just%20as%20likely%20to%20bump%20into%20a%20government%20leader%20as%20you%20are%20a%20tech%20billionaire.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20this%20year%3F%20The%20guest%20list%20has%20expanded.%20Brazil%2C%20Indonesia%2C%20Mongolia%2C%20and%20Korea%20have%20all%20joined%20the%20Davos%20scene%2C%20setting%20up%20their%20own%20hubs%20and%20signaling%20that%20they're%20ready%20to%20be%20heard.%20I've%20got%20meetings%20lined%20up%20with%20officials%20from%20these%20countries%2C%20and%20I'm%20curious%20to%20hear%20what's%20top%20of%20mind%20for%20them.%20One%20recurring%20theme%3F%20Donald%20Trump's%20reelection%20and%20what%20it%20could%20mean%20for%20the%20developing%20world.%20With%20global%20capital%20still%20flowing%20largely%20from%20the%20US%2C%20there's%20a%20lot%20at%20stake.%20Policies%20shaped%20in%20Washington%20have%20ripple%20effects%20from%20Jakarta%20to%20S%C3%A3o%20Paulo.%20The%20mood%20here%20suggests%20leaders%20aren't%20just%20watching%E2%80%94they're%20strategizing.%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3ESpriha%20Srivastava%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EDavos%20is%20known%20for%20its%20big%20parties.%20%3C%2Fspan%3EJPMorgan%20hosts%20one%20of%20the%20week's%20biggest%20blow-out%20events.%3Cspan%3E%20Google%2C%20Qualcomm%2C%20and%20others%20are%20also%20hosting%20big%20gatherings.%20CEOs%20and%20other%20folks%20on%20the%20ground%20tell%20me%20going%20to%20parties%20is%20the%20best%20way%20to%20network%20but%20say%20that%20the%20smaller%20parties%20can%20be%20best%20for%20meaningful%20conversations.%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3EHugh%20Langley%3C%2Fem%3E%3