%20to%20leave%20him%20out.%20But%20he%20was%20pitted%20against%20Rishabh%20Pant%2C%20who%20we%20all%20know%20can%20be%20a%20game-changer.%20Plus%20Pant%20is%20a%20left-hander%20and%20he%20is%20probably%20the%20better%20wicketkeeper%2C%20although%20he%20might%20not%20be%20the%20better%20batter%20than%20Samson%2C%26quot%3B%20Gavaskar%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DHLwovS3ABS0%5C%22%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Gavaskar%20explained%20the%20logic%20behind%20the%20selectors%20picking%20Pant%20over%20Samson%2C%20labelling%20the%20former%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bbetter%20keeper%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPant%20can%20change%20the%20game%20perhaps%20a%20little%20more%20than%20Samson%20and%20that's%20reason%20why%20Samson%20missed%20out.%20But%20Samson%20must%20not%20feel%20dejected%20because%20all%20Indian%20cricket%20lovers%20will%20have%20sympathy%20for%20him%20for%20what%20he%20has%20achieved%2C%26quot%3B%20Gavaskar%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20making%20his%20ODI%20debut%2C%20Samson%20has%20been%20in%20and%20out%20of%20team%2C%20with%20the%20selectors%20often%20ignoring%20him%20despite%20his%20stellar%20record%20in%20the%2050-over%20format.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20played%20just%2016%20ODIs%20in%20nearly%20a%20decade%2C%20scoring%20510%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2056.66%20and%20a%20strike-rate%20of%2099.60%20with%20a%20hundred%20and%20three%20fifties%20to%20show%20for%20his%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia's%20squad%20for%20Champions%20Trophy%202024%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20(C)%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shubman%20Gill%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F108578-shubman-gill-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShubman%20G