%5C%22Author%20Melissa%20Noble%20and%20her%20son%20at%20an%20ice%20cream%20shop%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67867ecb50dfd88e193e37d2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhen%20my%20kid%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20a%20life-threatening%20allergy%2C%20my%20family%20and%20community%20jumped%20into%20action.%20%3Cp%3EMelissa%20Noble%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20was%20terrified%20when%20my%20son%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20a%20life-threatening%20allergy%20to%20almonds.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20handled%20the%20diagnosis%20bravely%2C%20and%20our%20friends%20learned%20how%20to%20use%20EpiPens.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20no%20longer%20has%20this%20severe%20allergy%2C%20but%20the%20experience%20made%20me%20so%20grateful%20for%20our%20community.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20July%202023%2C%20my%208-year-old%20son%20and%20I%20were%20having%20a%20smoothie%20together%20in%20our%20small%20town%20in%20Australia%20when%20he%20started%20to%20complain%20that%20his%20throat%20felt%20strange.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20kept%20on%20saying%20that%20his%20tongue%20felt%20like%20it%20was%20getting%20bigger%2C%20and%20I%20noticed%20he%20had%20a%20red%20rash%20down%20his%20chin.%20Our%20doctor%20referred%20us%20to%20an%20allergy%20specialist%2C%20and%20by%20October%2C%20he'd%20gotten%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsigns-of-allergic-reaction-food-environment-2019-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eskin-prick%20test.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20revealed%20one%20of%20my%20worst%20fears%3A%20%3Cspan%3EOur%20son%20had%20a%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flife-threatening-food-allergies-daughter-future-live-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Elife-threatening%20allergy%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20almonds.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f2079e96-9144-4eb4-be7b-cc91708a7391%5C%22%3EOur%20whole%20world%20changed%20instantly%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAllergies%20such%20as%20this%20can%20cause%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fanaphylaxis%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eanaphylaxis%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20symptoms%20%3Cspan%3Ecan%20include%20difficulty%20breathing%2C%20coughing%2C%20fainting%2C%20severe%20stomach%20pain%2C%20and%20tongue%20or%20throat%20swelling%20%E2%80%94%20just%20like%20my%20son%20experienced.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20not%20treated%20immediately%2C%20anaphylaxis%20can%20be%20fatal.%20As%20I%20sat%20there%20listening%20to%20the%20prognosis%2C%20I%20couldn't%20believe%20it.%20No%20one%20in%20our%20families%20had%20ever%20had%20a%20severe%20allergy%20that%20we%20knew%20of%2C%20and%20I%20didn't%20know%20much%20about%20them%20at%20all.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20pediatric%20allergist%20gave%20us%20a%20referral%20for%20an%20EpiPen%20(an%20auto-injector%20used%20to%20treat%20life-threatening%2C%20allergic%20emergencies)%2C%20issued%20us%20with%20an%20action%20plan%20about%20what%20to%20do%20in%20the%20event%20of%20exposure%2C%20and%20said%20she'd%20see%20us%20in%2012%20months.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThose%20first%20few%20weeks%20after%20the%20diagnosis%2C%20I%20had%20terrible%20anxiety%20about%20the%20situation.%20I%20cried%20often%20and%20had%20nightmares%20about%20my%20son%20having%20a%20bad%20reaction.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kids%20playing%20on%20playground%20and%20slide%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67867f8f50dfd88e193e37f5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224008%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20worried%20what%20would%20happen%20if%20my%20kid%20had%20an%20allergic%20reaction%20and%20I%20wasn't%20there%20to%20help.%20%3Cp%3EFG%20Trade%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20began%20carrying%20an%20adrenaline%20injector%20and%20antihistamines%20with%20us%20every%20time%20we%20left%20the%20house.%20When%20my%20son%20ate%20something%20new%2C%20we'd%20check%20the%20labels%20meticulously%20for%20almonds%20in%20any%20form.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGrandparents%20were%20schooled%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-history-of-the-epipen-and-epinephrine-2016-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehow%20to%20use%20an%20EpiPen%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Friends%20offered%20to%20learn%20how%20to%20use%20one%20before%20a%20playdate%2C%20lest%20they%20should%20have%20to%20jab%20my%20son.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20started%20getting%20ahead%20of%20myself%20and%20worrying%20about%20the%20teenage%20years%20when%20my%20son%20might%20be%20drunk%20at%20a%20party%20and%20eat%20something%20without%20thinking%20or%20when%20he%20was%20older%20and%20traveling%2C%20unable%20to%20decipher%20ingredients%20in%20another%20language.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20a%20rough%20period%2C%20but%20my%20son%20handled%20it%20all%20like%20a%20champ.%20He%20would%20%3C%2Fspan%3Ereligiously%20%3Cspan%3Echeck%20every%20ingredient%20label%20himself%2C%20and%20he%20got%20into%20the%20habit%20of%20asking%20parents%20at%20birthday%20parties%20if%20the%20cake%20contained%20almonds.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22baf61bf3-fca6-404a-8758-fdb79847bff7%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20a%20year%2C%20it%20was%20time%20for%20the%20follow-up%20test%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%2012%20months%20of%20stress%2C%20we%20headed%20back%20to%20the%20allergy%20specialist%20for%20our%20follow-up%20appointment.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20I%20sat%20there%20watching%20my%20little%20boy's%20back%20flair%20up%20with%20a%20tapestry%20of%20different-sized%20welts%20(based%20on%20his%20reaction%20to%20the%20various%20skin-prick%20allergens)%2C%20I%20felt%20terrified.%20What%20would%20this%20test%20reveal%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20interesting%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20pediatric%20allergist%20said%2C%20just%20as%20my%20heart%20felt%20like%20it%20was%20going%20to%20leap%20out%20of%20my%20chest.%20%26quot%3BHis%20almond%20reaction%20is%20half%20of%20what%20it%20was%20last%20year.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20suggested%20my%20son%20do%20an%20%26quot%3Balmond%20challenge%2C%26quot%3B%20in%20which%20they'd%20introduce%20small%20amounts%20of%20the%20nut%20into%20his%20system%20in%20a%20controlled%20setting.%20We%20agreed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20the%20big%20day%20arrived%2C%20I%20asked%20my%20son%20how%20he%20felt.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20scared%2C%20mummy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'll%20be%20all%20right.%26quot%3B%20As%20he%20drove%20with%20my%20husband%20to%20the%20allergist's%20office%2C%20I%20kept%20thinking%20how%20brave%20he%20was%2C%20even%20at%20such%20a%20young%20age.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20day%2C%20I%20could%20barely%20concentrate%20at%20work%20until%20my%20husband%20called%20with%20the%20best%20news%20of%20my%20life%3A%20Our%20son%20hadn't%20reacted.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETears%20streamed%20down%20my%20face.%20I%20felt%20so%20overwhelmed%20with%20gratitude%2C%20but%20we%20still%20weren't%20quite%20out%20of%20the%20woods%20yet.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20seven%20days%20after%2C%20my%20son%20was%20instructed%20to%20eat%20a%20small%20amount%20of%20almonds%20a%20day%20at%20home%20and%20note%20any%20reactions.%20When%20there%20was%20nothing%20to%20report%2C%20he%20was%20given%20the%20all%20clear.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20mark%20a%20week%20of%20no%20reactions%2C%20I%20gave%20my%20son%20my%20full%20blessing%20to%20give%20his%20former%20arch-enemy%20%E2%80%94%20the%20almond%20%E2%80%94%20the%20middle%20finger%2C%20and%20our%20family%20had%20a%20good%20chuckle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f792540c-bae6-428d-b075-1d4137506c71%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20found%20a%20silver%20lining%20in%20a%20stressful%20experience%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOnly%20a%20very%20small%20percentage%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rch.org.au%2FuploadedFiles%2FMain%2FContent%2Fallergy%2FTree%2520Nut%2520Allergy.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echildren%20with%20an%20allergy%20to%20tree%20nuts%3C%2Fa%3E%20outgrow%20them.%20It%20seems%20my%20son%20was%20one%20of%20the%20lucky%20ones%20(or%20maybe%20there%20was%20another%20reason%20his%20initial%20skin-prick%20test%20was%20so%20elevated%2C%20we'll%20never%20know%20for%20sure).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20severe%20allergy%20diagnosis%20really%20does%20rock%20your%20world%2C%20and%20I%20feel%20for%20others%20who%20have%20to%20navigate%20those%20turbulent%20waters.%20Through%20this%20experience%2C%20though%2C%20I%20learned%20a%20lot%20about%20the%20value%20of%20true%20community%20and%20friendship.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20friends%20made%20separate%20cakes%20just%20for%20our%20son%2C%20checked%20ingredient%20lists%20like%20forensic%20detectives%2C%20and%20stepped%20up%20when%20given%20an%20EpiPen%20to%20potentially%20use.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20realized%20that%20bravery%20comes%20in%20all%20shapes%20and%20sizes%20and%20that%20we%20can%20often%20learn%20so%20much%20from%20our%20children.%20When%20presented%20with%20a%20scary%20situation%2C%20my%20young%20son%20faced%20it%20with%20courage%20%E2%80%94%20perhaps%20we%20could%20all%20use%20a%20little%20more%20of%20that.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkid-diagnosed-with-life-threatening-allergy-how-what-we-did-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737374041000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67868160e294a7514e8cec01%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%