20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%20relating%20to%20rape%20and%20murder.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%2C%20the%20court%20heard%20Roy%20and%20final%20arguments%20on%20the%20sentence.%20Addressing%20the%20court%2C%20Roy%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20haven't%20done%20this.%20I%20have%20been%20framed.%20Lots%20of%20things%20were%20destroyed%2C%20but%20if%20I%20had%20done%20it%20then%20my%20rudraksha%20mala%20would%20have%20broken.%20You%20decide%20whether%20I%20have%20been%20framed%20or%20not.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20replied%20that%20he%20had%20to%20deliver%20justice.%20%26quot%3BI%20decide%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20evidence%20before%20me.%20I%20have%20heard%20you%20as%20well%20for%20three%20hours.%20Your%20lawyer%20has%20argued%20your%20case.%20The%20charges%20has%20been%20proved.%20Now%20I%20want%20to%20know%20your%20views%20on%20the%20punishment%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%2C%20which%20took%20over%20the%20investigation%20from%20Kolkata%20Police%2C%20had%20demanded%20death%20penalty%20for%20Roy%2C%20who%20worked%20as%20a%20civic%20volunteer%20and%20frequented%20the%20hospital.%20Counsel%20representing%20the%20CBI%20and%20the%20victim's%20parents%20said%20this%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Brarest%20of%20rare%20cases%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20Roy%20must%20be%20sentenced%20to%20death.%20Roy's%20lawyer%20had%20cited%20Supreme%20Court%20guidelines%20on%20awarding%20death%20penalty.%20The%20judge%20then%20asked%20the%20counsel%20to%20list%20down%20the%20guidelines%20so%20that%20he%20could%20take%20a%20look%20at%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20premises%20in%20Sealdah%20have%20been%20turned%20into%20a%20fortress%20as%20police%20went%20all%20out%20to%20prevent%20any%20untoward%20incident%20after%20sentencing.%20Despite%20being%20denied%20permission%2C%20doctors%20and%20others%20gathered%20near%20the%20court.%20The%20protesters%20alleged%20that%20Roy%20alone%20could%20not%20have%20committed%20the%20crime%20and%20that%20the%20others%20should%20not%20escape%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victim's%20parents%20have%20said%20they%20are%20not%20satisfied%20with%20the%20CBI's%20investigation.%20They%20have%20alleged%20that%20%26quot%3Bother%20perpetrators%20involved%20in%20the%20crime%20had%20not%20been%20brought%20to%20justice%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BOnly%20one%20person%20is%20not%20involved%20in%20the%20crime%2C%20yet%20the%20CBI%20has%20failed%20to%20apprehend%20the%20others.%20Such%20criminals%20have%20no%20right%20to%20live%20if%20we%20are%20to%20prevent%20future%20crimes%20in%20society%2C%26quot%3B%20her%20mother%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2034-year-old%20doctor%2C%20a%20postgraduate%20trainee%20at%20the%20hospital%2C%20was%20on%20night%20shift%20on%20the%20day%20of%20incident.%20The%20next%20morning%2C%20she%20was%20found%20dead%20in%20a%20seminar%20room%20of%20the%20hospital.%20The%20incident%20sparked%20nationwide%20protests%2C%20with%20doctors%20suspending%20work%20for%20days%20to%20demand%20safety%20at%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737370980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fbf8k857_sanjoy-roy_625x300_20_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frg-kar-hospital-rape-murder-convict-sanjay-roy-gets-life-sentence-7516087%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22RG%20Kar%20Hospital%20Rape-Murder%20Convict%20Sanjay%20Roy%20Gets%20Life%20Sentence%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frg-kar-hospital-rape-murder-convict-sanjay-roy-gets-life-sentence-7516087%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Today's%20Mortgage%20Rates%20%7C%20Mortgage%20Rates%20May%20Rise%20Under%20Trump%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20offers%20and%20details%20on%20this%20page%20may%20have%20updated%20or%20changed%20since%20the%20time%20of%20publication.%20See%20our%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%