E%3Cp%3EI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdaughter-graduated-high-school-didnt-enroll-college-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edidn't%20go%20to%20college%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20graduating%20from%20high%20school.%20Instead%2C%20I%20started%20applying%20for%20work%20right%20away%20in%202005.%20I%20enjoy%20tech%2C%20video%20games%2C%20and%20Star%20Wars%2C%20so%20I%20wanted%20to%20get%20a%20job%20in%20that%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20became%20good%20at%20interviewing%20by%20doing%20group%20interviews%20and%20seeing%20what%20others%20did%2C%20and%20I%20landed%20a%20position%20doing%20quality%20assurance%20for%20LucasArts.%20I%20had%20a%20six-month%20contract%20to%20work%20on%20the%20video%20game%20Star%20Wars%20Battlefront%20II.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20landed%20more%20contract%20roles%20at%20Electronic%20Arts%2C%20Friend%20Finder%2C%20and%20eventually%20companies%20like%20Meta%20and%20TikTok.%20For%20my%20first%20few%20contract%20roles%2C%20I%20was%20living%20in%20California.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20some%20of%20my%20more%20recent%20contracts%2C%20I%20worked%20remotely%20from%20Mexico%20without%20telling%20anyone%20%E2%80%94%20and%20got%20away%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fa598eae-8cb4-46fd-aeb8-783cf011e348%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhile%20working%20at%20Friend%20Finder%2C%20I%20took%20my%20first%20international%20trip%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20pay%20at%20Friend%20Finder%20was%20enough%20to%20take%20my%20first%20international%20trip%20to%20Tokyo%2C%20which%20started%20my%20love%20for%20travel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20stayed%20at%20Friend%20Finder%20until%202008%20and%20then%20got%20a%20great%20opportunity%20%E2%80%94%20my%20first%20full-time%20job%20at%20Apple%20in%20the%20App%20Store%20division.%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-software-engineer-left-after-2-years-side-hustle-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworked%20at%20Apple's%20headquarters%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%