20patio%20heaters%20before%20the%20pandemic.%20I%20mean%2C%20I%20knew%20they%20existed%2C%20but%20I%20hadn't%20really%20%3Cem%3Ethought%20%3C%2Fem%3Eabout%20them.%20During%20the%20pandemic%2C%20I%20thought%20about%20them%20too%20much%20%E2%80%94%20where%20they%20were%2C%20where%20they%20weren't%2C%20whether%20they%20worked.%20Where%20there's%20a%20will%2C%20there's%20a%20way%2C%20and%20in%202020%20and%202021%20I%20had%20All%20The%20Will%20to%20leave%20my%20apartment%20and%20socialize%20on%20cold%20New%20York%20City%20days.%20That%20meant%20any%20trip%20to%20a%20restaurant%20or%20bar%20entailed%20careful%20consideration%20of%20the%20outdoor%20heat%20situation.%20I%20kept%20mental%20rankings%20of%20the%20various%20types.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-patio-heater%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20outdoor%20heater%3C%2Fa%3E%20I%20experienced%20was%20a%20little%20propane%20guy%20at%20a%20restaurant%20in%20Philadelphia%20that%20was%20sneakily%20effective.%20The%20worst%20was%20one%20of%20those%20tower%20ones%20at%20a%20wine%20bar%20down%20the%20street%20%E2%80%94%20the%20owner%20had%20put%20it%20under%20an%20umbrella%20in%20the%20rain%2C%20and%20it%20caught%20on%20fire.%20That%20glass%20of%20pinot%20grigio%20came%20at%20a%20very%20cold%2C%20wet%20expense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20pandemic%20subsided%20and%20people%20returned%20to%20the%20great%20indoors%2C%20I%20assumed%20patio%20heaters%20would%20largely%20disappear%2C%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcoronavirus-panic-buying-toilet-paper-stockpiling-photos-2020-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etoilet-paper%20hoarding%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvideos-people-cities-cheering-healthcare-workers-windows-rooftops-same-time-2020-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclapping%20for%20essential%20workers%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20they've%20stuck%20around%2C%20becoming%20fixtures%20at%20restaurants%20and%20bars%20and%20hotels%20and%20people's%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShutdowns%20of%20gathering%20places%20and%20lockdowns%20that%20kept%20people%20at%20home%20fostered%20a%20new%20appreciation%20for%20the%20outdoors.%20It%20sparked%20a%20greater%20openness%20to%20spending%20more%20time%20outside%20even%20when%20the%20temperature%20isn't%20a%20perfect%2072%20degrees%20Fahrenheit.%20And%20a%20lot%20of%20homeowners%20rethought%20the%20utility%20of%20their%20spaces%2C%20which%20led%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhome-improvement-boom-housing-market-recovery-millennials-pandemic-2021-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epandemic-driven%20surge%20in%20renovations%3C%2Fa%3E%20featuring%20new%20patios%20and%20decks%20they'd%20very%20much%20like%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20year-round.%20Your%20mileage%20may%20vary%20on%20how%20effective%20these%20devices%20are%20%E2%80%94%20no%20heater%20is%20going%20to%20get%20you%20sitting%20outside%20comfortably%20in%20Chicago%20in%20February%2C%20and%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20variation%20in%20quality%20across%20products.%20But%20heaters%20are%20ubiquitous%2C%20and%20they're%20not%20going%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20establishments%20such%20as%20restaurants%20and%20bars%2C%20keeping%20patrons%20warm%20outdoors%20was%20a%20key%20part%20of%20survival.%20For%20people%20bored%20at%20home%2C%20a%20patio%20heater%20became%20a%20way%20to%20keep%20themselves%20from%20going%20stir-crazy.%20While%20businesses%20and%20consumers%20aren't%20scooping%20up%20patio%20heaters%20at%20the%20rate%20they%20were%20four%20years%20ago%20(or%20enduring%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbsnews.com%2Fnews%2Famazon-pandemic-pricing-patio-heater%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccompanying%20price%20gouging%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20they're%20still%20buying%20them%20more%20than%20they%20were%20before%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdobe%2C%20which%20tracks%20online%20sales%20during%20holidays%20and%20major%20shopping%20events%20such%20as%20Black%20Friday%20and%20Cyber%20Monday%2C%20found%20patio%20and%20outdoor%20heaters%20were%20still%20a%20hot%20seller%20last%20year.%20Spending%20on%20the%20items%20ramped%20up%20earlier%20in%202024%20than%20it%20did%20in%202023%2C%20likely%20driven%20by%20deeper%20and%20earlier%20discounts%20on%20appliances.%20Cyber%20Week%20sales%20of%20outdoor%20heaters%20were%20up%20by%20314%25%20over%20daily%20average%20sales%20in%20October%2C%20compared%20with%20262%25%20for%20appliances%20overall.%20Tabletop%20and%20portable%20models%20in%20particular%20were%20popular.%20Vivek%20Pandya%2C%20a%20lead%20analyst%20at%20Adobe%20Digital%20Insights%2C%20says%20it's%20not%20just%20first-time%20buyers%20scooping%20patio%20heaters%20up%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20repeat%20purchasers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20think%20about%20the%20pandemic%2C%20we're%20about%20four%20years%20outside%20of%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20then%20have%20a%20cycle%20where%20maybe%20consumers%20are%20replacing%20certain%20items%20or%20interested%20in%20getting%20certain%20items.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20Trends%20suggests%20that%20searches%20for%20patio%20heaters%20usually%20pick%20up%20in%20the%20fall%20as%20people%20prepare%20for%20the%20cold%20months%20ahead.%20While%20search%20interest%20is%20well%20below%20where%20it%20was%20in%20the%20fall%20of%202020%2C%20it%20remains%20elevated%20from%20where%20it%20was%20before%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEric%20Kahn%2C%20the%20founder%20and%20director%20of%20Alfresco%20Heating%2C%20which%20specializes%20in%20patio%20and%20outdoor%20heating%2C%20saw%20sales%20fall%20after%202020%20as%20consumers%20shifted%20their%20spending%20toward%20traveling%20and%20dining%20out%20rather%20than%20beefing%20up%20their%20homes.%20He%20thought%202024%20would%20be%20his%20third%20consecutive%20year%20of%20a%20decline%20in%20gross%20sales%2C%20but%20a%20big%20bump%20in%20the%20fall%20salvaged%20his%20year.%20The%20season%20was%20%26quot%3Beven%20pandemic-level%20strong%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20and%20business%20remains%20above%20the%20pre-pandemic%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20overall%20numbers%20are%20about%20halfway%20between%20what%20they%20peaked%20out%20at%20the%20pandemic%20and%20what%20they%20were%20before%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Kahn%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELeah%20Langford%2C%20a%20marketing%20manager%20at%20Bromic%20Heating%2C%20told%20me%20the%20company%20saw%20a%20%26quot%3Bhuge%20boom%26quot%3B%20in%20sales%20of%20its%20outdoor%20heaters%20during%20the%20pandemic.%20It's%20always%20done%20solid%20business%20on%20the%20commercial%20side%2C%20but%20residential%20interest%20in%20heaters%20took%20off%2C%20too%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it's%20stuck.%20%26quot%3BResidential%20is%20where%20we're%20seeing%20the%20biggest%20boom%2C%20and%20really%20our%20focus%20right%20now%20is%20homeowners%20and%20educating%20on%20the%20different%20types%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20just%20really%20shifted%20the%20awareness%20that%20they%20exist.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20greater%20awareness%20of%20the%20possibilities%20of%20outdoor%20spaces%20(and%20the%20importance%20of%20heating)%20has%20shifted%20Tara%20L.%20Paige's%20life%20and%20career.%20During%20the%20pandemic%2C%20she%20created%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fblackwomenwholoveoutdoorlivingspaces%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFacebook%20page%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20Black%20women%20who%20love%20outdoor%20living%20spaces.%20It%20now%20has%20nearly%20250%2C000%20members.%20Paige%20grew%20up%20as%20what%20she%20described%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Boutside%20girl%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20her%20dad%20always%20had%20a%20fire%20burning%20outside%20%E2%80%94%20but%20she's%20aware%20that's%20not%20true%20for%20everyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20pandemic%20opened%20up%20everybody's%20world%20and%20to%20being%20able%20to%20extend%20their%20inside%20to%20their%20outside.%20And%20now%20it's%20like%2C%20OK%2C%20patio%20heaters%20are%20essential%2C%20fire%20pits%20are%20essential%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20started%20sitting%20outside%20and%20feeling%20like%2C%20man%2C%20this%20is%20freedom%2C%20this%20feels%20good.%20And%20just%20because%20it's%20cold%20outside%2C%20I%20don't%20have%20to%20stop.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPaige%20created%20an%20outdoor-living%20lifestyle%20brand%2C%20The%20Patieaux%20Chick%2C%20and%20is%20launching%20her%20own%20line%20of%20patio%20furniture.%20She's%20not%20doing%20heaters%2C%20but%20she's%20got%20thoughts%20on%20them%2C%20especially%20living%20in%20a%20windy%20part%20of%20Texas.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20looking%20for%20one%20that's%20really%20sturdy%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20Otherwise%2C%20the%20right%20wind%20gets%20it%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bit'll%20knock%20the%20whole%20thing%20over.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20people%20are%20still%20buying%20patio%20heaters%2C%20what's%20not%20clear%20is%20whether%20they're%20buying%20%3Cem%3Egood%3C%2Fem%3E%20ones.%20There's%20a%20ton%20of%20variation%20%E2%80%94%20propane%20or%20infrared%2C%20portable%20or%20permanent%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it's%20tough%20to%20know%20whether%20you're%20getting%20bang%20for%20your%20buck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20learn%20the%20lay%20of%20the%20land%2C%20I%20reached%20out%20to%20Thom%20Dunn%2C%20a%20writer%20for%20Wirecutter%2C%20The%20New%20York%20Times'%20product-recommendation%20section%2C%20who%20focuses%20on%20home%20heating%20and%20cooling.%20He%20said%20there%20are%20generally%20two%20options%20for%20heaters%20he%20focuses%20on%3A%20the%20propane%20ones%2C%20where%20you%20sort%20of%20see%20actual%20flames%2C%20and%20the%20red%20radiant%20ones.%20The%20former%20keep%20you%20warm%20%26quot%3Bas%20much%20as%20a%20fire%20could%20keep%20you%20warm%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20so%20they%20do%20better%20when%20you're%20huddled%20around%20it.%20The%20latter%20feel%20better%20when%20they're%20directly%20on%20you%2C%20like%20the%20rays%20of%20the%20sun%2C%20but%20they%20warm%20only%20the%20parts%20of%20your%20body%20they%20hit.%20He%20prefers%20the%20kind%20with%20an%20elongated%2C%20vertical%20glass%20tube%20and%20flame%20that%20shoots%20up%20the%20middle%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20nice%20to%20gather%20around%20for%20parties.%20%26quot%3BWith%20the%20fire%20tube%2C%20it%20feels%20more%20welcoming%2C%20to%20be%20like%2C%20cool%2C%20let's%20sit%20out%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20But%20maybe%20a%20red%20heat%20lamp%20on%20the%20wall%20is%20fine%20if%20someone%20wants%20to%20stand%20outside%20for%20a%20bit%20to%20smoke%20a%20cigarette%20or%20something.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20fine%20to%20get%20a%20little%20warmth%20on%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20I'm%20not%20going%20to%20stay%20outside.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKahn%2C%20from%20Alfresco%20Heating%2C%20told%20me%20he%20doesn't%20usually%20recommend%20the%20tube%20ones.%20While%20the%20aesthetic%20is%20nice%2C%20they%20don't%20do%20much%20heat-wise%2C%20in%20part%20because%20the%20glass%20acts%20as%20an%20insulator.%20But%20the%20real%20bane%20of%20his%20existence%20is%20the%20cheap%20portable%20heaters%20people%20buy%20online.%20He%20jokingly%20refers%20to%20them%20as%20%26quot%3Bdisposable%20lighters.%26quot%3B%20The%20low-quality%20options%20often%20end%20up%20breaking%20after%20a%20year%20or%20two%2C%20meaning%20consumers%20get%20stuck%20in%20a%20cycle%20of%20buying%20bad%20product%20after%20bad%20product%20instead%20of%20just%20investing%20in%20one%20decent%20one.%20%26quot%3BThey%20think%20they're%20junk%2C%20so%20they're%20buying%20junk%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOverall%2C%20if%20people%20are%20wanting%20a%20good%20experience%20for%20a%20long%20period%20of%20time%2C%20then%20investing%20in%20permanent%20%E2%80%94%20particularly%20overhead%20%E2%80%94%20patio%20heaters%20can%20be%20a%20very%20worthwhile%20investment%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20sai