0To%20Come%20To%20Supreme%20Court%20For%20Father's%20Burial%26quot%3B%3A%20A%20Shocking%20Bastar%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20Chhattisgarh%20man's%20body%20is%20waiting%20in%20the%20mortuary%20for%20a%20court%20order%20that%20will%20clear%20the%20roadblocks%20in%20its%20burial.%20Subhash%20Baghel's%20body%20is%20in%20the%20morgue%20for%20the%20past%2012%20days%20after%20some%20residents%20of%20his%20village%20in%20Bastar%20stopped%20his%20family%20members%20from%20burying%20him%20in%20the%20village%20burial%20ground%20because%20they%20had%20converted%20to%20Christianity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubhash's%20son%20Ramesh%20Baghel%20has%20now%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20seeking%20permission%20to%20bury%20his%20father%20next%20to%20his%20ancestors.%20Hearing%20the%20matter%2C%20the%20bench%20of%20Justice%20BV%20Nagarathna%20and%20Justice%20Satish%20Chandra%20Sharma%20made%20strong%20remarks.%20%26quot%3BWhy%20can't%20a%20person%20be%20buried%20where%20they%20wanted%20to%20be%3F%20The%20body%20is%20in%20mortuary%3F%20we%20are%20sorry%20to%20say%20that%20a%20person%20has%20to%20come%20to%20Supreme%20Court%20for%20the%20burial%20of%20his%20father.%20The%20High%20Court%2C%20the%20panchayat%20etc%20are%20not%20able%20to%20solve%20the%20problem.%20The%20High%20Court%20says%20there%20will%20be%20a%20law%20and%20order%20problem.%20We%20are%20pained%20at%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Nagarathna%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESolicitor%20General%20Tushar%20Mehta%20said%20he%20did%20not%20have%20anything%20to%20say%20if%20the%20matter%20was%20to%20be%20decided%20solely%20on%20emotions%2C%20but%20if%20not%2C%20it%20can%20be%20argued.%20Senior%20Advocate%20Colin%20Gonsalves%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20petitioner%2C%20said%20the%20real%20reason%20for%20refusing%20burial%20was%20because%20the%20tribal%20family%20converted%20to%20Christianity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Solicitor%20General%20said%20this%20was%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bmovement%26quot%