uot%3Banti-fungal%26quot%3B%20properties%2C%20and%20can%20heal%20a%20variety%20of%20illnesses%2C%20including%20IBS%2C%20or%20Irritable%20Bowel%20Syndrome%20-%20advice%20apparently%20proffered%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fv-kamakoti%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EV%20Kamakoti%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Director%20of%20Chennai's%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%2C%20according%20to%20a%20video%20that%20emerged%20online%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20outrage%20over%20his%20comment%2C%20NDTV%20asked%20Professor%20Kamakoti%20this%20morning%20if%20someone%20who%20should%20be%20propagating%20science%20and%20a%20scientific%20temperament%20should%20spread%20superstition.%20To%20this%20he%20replied%2C%C2%A0%26quot%3BThe%20anti-fungal%2C%20anti-bacterial%2C%20and%20anti-inflammatory%20properties%20of%20cow%20urine%20have%20been%20scientifically%20demonstrated...%20top%20journals%20in%20the%20United%20States%20have%20published%20scientific%20evidence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProf.%20Kamakoti%20-%20whose%20research%20interests%20include%20computational%20geometry%2C%20according%20to%20the%20website%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cse.iitm.ac.in%2Fprofile.php%3Farg%3DMTg%3D%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIIT%20Madras'%20Department%20of%20Computer%20Science%20and%20Engineering%3C%2Fa%3E%20-%20also%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20%26quot%3Bperception%20there%20is%20no%20strong%20experimentation%2C%20or%20scientific%20evidence%2C%20on%20the%20medicinal%20properties%20of%20on%20cow%20urine%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20shared%20a%20write-up%20published%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs41598-021-91684-4%23Sec10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENature%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20respected%20weekly%20scientific%20journal%2C%20in%20June%202021%2C%20in%20which%20scientists%20associated%20with%20the%20Animal%20Biotechnology%20Centre%20and%20Cell%20Biology%20and%20Proteomics%20Lab%20of%20the%20National%20Dairy%20Research%20Institute%2C%20had%20published%20the%20result%20of%20%26quot%3Bpeptide%20profiling%20in%20cow%20urine%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20authors%20concluded%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20presented%20a%20simple%20method%20for%20the%20discovery%20of%20thousands%20of%20endogenous%20peptides%20in%20cow%20urine%20that%20contribute%20to%20various%20bioactivities%20associated%20with%20urine...%20we%20provided%20evidence%20for%20the%20peptide-mediated%20antimicrobial%20activity%20against%20%3Cem%3EE.%20coli%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3ES.%20aureus%3C%2Fem%3E%20but%20more%20experiments%20are%20needed%20to%20validate%20other%20predicted%20bioactivities...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20according%20to%20his%20office%2C%20Professor%20Kamakoti%2C%20who%20is%20also%20an%20organic%20farmer%2C%C2%A0was%20merely%20%26quot%3Bsharing%20his%20own%20experiences%20in%20this%20event%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EIIT%20Madras%20Director's%20'Cow%20Urine'%20Remark%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20video%20in%20question%2C%20Mr%20Kamakoti%20-%20standing%20before%20a%20poster%20of%20a%20cow%20at%20an%20event%20celebrating%20the%20harvest%20festival%20of%20Pongal%20-%20narrates%20the%20story%20of%20a%20'sanyasi'%20who%20cured%20himself%20by%20drinking%20'%3Cem%3Egaumutra%3C%2Fem%3E'%2C%20or%20cow%20urine%2C%20and%20declares%2C%20to%20scattered%20applause%2C%20%26quot%3B...%20we%20have%20to%20accept%20its%20medicinal%20value%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EPeddling%20pseudoscience%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fiitmadras%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40iitmadras%3C%2Fa%3E%20Director%20is%20most%20unbecoming%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIMAIndiaOrg%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40IMAIndiaOrg%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FukB0jwBh8G%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FukB0jwBh8G%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Karti%20P%20Chidambaram%20(%40KartiPC)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FKartiPC%2Fstatus%2F1880567902656704894%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2018%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20a%20sanyasi...%20he%20had%20a%20high%20fever%2C%20and%20the%20people%20wanted%20to%20call%20a%20doctor.%20But%20the%20sanyasi%2C%20whose%20name%20I%20forget%2C%20he%20said%20(in%20Sanskrit)%2C%20'%3Cu%3Egaumutra%20%3C%2Fu%3E%3Cem%3Epibami%3C%2Fem%3E'%20and%20went%20immediately%20to%20a%20cowshed%20and%20got%20some%20cow%20urine.%20He%20drank%20this%20all%20down%20and%2C%20in%2015%20minutes%2C%20his%20fever%20disappeared.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo...%20(it%20has)%20anti-bacterial%20and%20anti-fungal%20(properties)...%20for%20digestive%20and%20stomach%20problems%2C%20for%20IBS...%20for%20many%20other%20illnesses%2C%20this%20'%3Cem%3Egaumutra%3C%2Fem%3E'%20is%20big%20medicine%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kamakoti%20declared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20news%20agency%20PTI%2C%20the%20comment%20-%20which%20sources%20in%20IIT%20(Madras)%20confirmed%20had%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20been%20made%20-%20was%20delivered%20at%20a%20'%3Cem%3Emattu%3C%2Fem%3E'%2C%20or%20'cow'%2C%20Pongal%20event%20in%20Chennai%20on%20January%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECongress%2C%20DMK's%20Sharp%20Reactions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20comment%20has%20been%20panned%20by%20political%20leaders%2C%20academics%2C%20and%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Karti%20Chidambaram%2C%20who%20flagged%20the%20remark%20to%20the%20Indian%20Medical%20Association%2C%20has%20criticised%20the%20IIT%20(Madras)%20chief%20for%20%26quot%3Bpeddling%20pseudoscience%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3B...%20most%20unbecoming%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETamil%20Nadu's%20ruling%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20has%20also%20slammed%20the%20IIT%20Madras%20boss%20and%20