he%20could%20take%20a%20look%20at%20it.%20The%20court%20will%20now%20assemble%20at%202.45%20pm%20to%20announce%20the%20sentence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20premises%20in%20Sealdah%20have%20been%20turned%20into%20a%20fortress%20as%20police%20go%20all%20out%20to%20prevent%20any%20untoward%20incident%20after%20that%20sentencing.%20Despite%20being%20denied%20permission%2C%20doctors%20and%20others%20have%20gathered%20near%20the%20court.%20The%20protesters%20are%20alleging%20that%20Roy%20alone%20could%20not%20have%20committed%20the%20crime%20and%20that%20the%20others%20should%20not%20escape%20justice.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victim's%20parents%20have%20said%20they%20are%20not%20satisfied%20with%20the%20CBI's%20investigation.%20They%20have%20alleged%20that%20%26quot%3Bother%20perpetrators%20involved%20in%20the%20crime%20had%20not%20been%20brought%20to%20justice%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%E2%80%9COnly%20one%20person%20is%20not%20involved%20in%20the%20crime%2C%20yet%20the%20CBI%20has%20failed%20to%20apprehend%20the%20others.%20Such%20criminals%20have%20no%20right%20to%20live%20if%20we%20are%20to%20prevent%20future%20crimes%20in%20society%2C%E2%80%9D%20her%20mother%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2034-year-old%20doctor%2C%20a%20postgraduate%20trainee%20at%20the%20hospital%2C%20was%20on%20night%20shift%20on%20the%20day%20of%20incident.%20The%20next%20morning%2C%20she%20was%20found%20dead%20in%20a%20seminar%20room%20of%20the%20hospital.%20The%20incident%20sparked%20nationwide%20protests%2C%20with%20doctors%20suspending%20work%20for%20days%20to%20demand%20safety%20at%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737360120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fbf8k857_sanjoy-roy_625x300_20_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkolkata-rape-murder-case-kolkata-doctor-rape-murder-kolkata-rape-murder-convict-says-he-has-been-framed-what-judge-replied-7515306%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%