V%2C%20fridge%2C%20sofa%2C%20washing%20machine%2C%20oven%2C%20and%20even%20a%20mixer%20to%20collect%20money%20for%20the%20research.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20research%20and%20development%20process%20took%20two%20years.%20During%20this%20period%2C%20Siddharth%20met%20Alvin%20in%20a%20chance%20business%20meeting.%20Both%20shared%20the%20same%20vision%20of%20a%20more%20sustainable%20world%20and%20a%20plastic-free%20Kerala%E2%80%94their%20homeland.%20Inspired%20by%20their%20shared%20goals%2C%20Siddharth%2C%20Alvin%2C%20and%20Sooraj%20decided%20to%20join%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trio%20formally%20launched%20Carbon%20%26amp%3B%20Whale%20in%202022.%20Their%20approach%20involves%20meticulously%20collecting%20and%20sorting%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F263044%2Fifs-officer-madhya-pradesh-plastic-waste-electricity-biogas-employment%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplastic%20waste%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewith%20the%20help%20of%20local%20school%20and%20college%20volunteers%20and%20non-profit%20organisations.%20The%20collected%20waste%20is%20then%20sorted%20by%20type%20and%20quality%20before%20undergoing%20a%20specialised%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F311038%2Fmani-vajipey-raj-madangopal-banyan-nation-hyderabad-recycle-plastic-waste-into-fmcg-bottles-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecycling%20process%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20process%20breaks%20down%20the%20plastic%20into%20usable%20components%2C%20which%20are%20moulded%20into%20benches%20and%20paver%20tiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3