9CThe%20paver%20tile%20has%20more%20strength%20than%20a%20normal%20interlock%20made%20of%20concrete.%20This%20is%20one%20of%20our%20USPs%20(Unique%20Selling%20Point).%20There%20is%20also%20no%20issue%20of%20wear%20and%20tear%20or%20rusting%2C%20which%20is%20common%20in%20metal%20benches.%20If%20anything%20happens%20to%20the%20recycled%20material%2C%20we%20can%20recycle%20it%20again.%20As%20these%20are%20made%20of%20plastic%2C%20they%20are%20durable%20and%20protected%20from%20termite%20damage%2C%20unlike%20wooden%20furniture.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20interlock%20paver%20tiles%20and%20public%20benches%20have%20already%20been%20installed%20in%20several%20malls%20and%20metro%20stations%20across%20Kerala%20and%20Bengaluru.%20Interestingly%2C%20the%20friends%20have%20partnered%20with%20LuLu%20Group%2C%20HiLITE%20group%2C%20Cochin%20Smart%20Mission%20Limited%20(CSML)%2C%20Malabar%20Group%2C%20Centre%20Square%20Mall%20Kochi%2C%20Kochi%20Metro%2C%20and%20Kerala%20Tourism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETurning%2010%2C000%20kg%20of%20plastic%20into%20purpose%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20two%20years%2C%20the%20company%20claims%20to%20have%20saved%2010%2C000%20kg%20of%20plastic%20waste%20from%20polluting%20landfills%20and%20oceans.%20Siddharth%20mentions%20that%20their%20mission%20is%20to%20declutter%20one%20million%20kilograms%20of%20plastic%20waste%20in%20Kerala%20as%20part%20of%20their%20ongoing%20campaign%2C%20%23Declutter.%20%E2%80%9CSo%20far%2C%20we%20have%20successfully%20transformed%203%2C000%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F325564%2Fthe-disposal-company-bhagyashree-bhansali-waste-plastic-cre